<sect1 id="md_documents_markdown-vs-rest_1autotoc_md5">
<title>ToC tree</title>
<para>in reST:</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">..<sp/>toctree::</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>:maxdepth:<sp/>1</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>:caption:<sp/>ToC<sp/>title</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>:titlesonly:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>:glob:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>:hidden:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>...</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>link<sp/>text<sp/>&lt;./path/link.format&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>...</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>in MD-MyST:</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">\```{toctree}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">---</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">maxdepth:<sp/>2</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">caption:<sp/>ToC<sp/>title</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">titlesonly:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">glob:<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">hidden:<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">---</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">link<sp/>text<sp/>&lt;./path/link.format&gt;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>reST<sp/>codeblocks</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>.. code-block:: :caption: a code block caption</para>
<para>import rospy </para>
